snippet.title: Emio – The Smiling Man: Famicom Detective Club Teaser - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Pre-order Emio – The Smiling Man: Famicom Detective Club: https://www.nintendo.com/us/store/products/emio-the-smiling-man-famicom-detective-club-switch/?utm_source=SW-AA&utm_medium=soytnoa&utm_campaign=N1139-01&utm_id=N1139-01

Unmask the truth in a dark, twisted thriller for Nintendo Switch. Emio – The Smiling Man: Famicom Detective Club launches August 29th.
